{"word":"ἐκτρέπω","slug":"ἐκτρέπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐϰτρέπω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a>, τρέπω</el>] ‘turn out of a normal course or position’, <b>veer off <a href='B:610 6:20'>1 Ti 6:20</a>; turn away <a href='B:610 1:6'>1:6</a>; <a href='B:610 5:15'>5:15</a>; <a href='B:620 4:4'>2 Ti 4:4</a>;</b> in imagery of a lame leg, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> viewed as potentially more askew than before, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b>dislocate</b> (in effect = ‘be dislocated’) <b><a href='B:650 12:13'>Hb 12:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκτός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκτρέφω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}